analysis: The agent omitted the required "contactMethod": "Email" parameter in its function call, resulting in a parameter mismatch that caused the evaluator not to recognize the function call as correct.

The agent supplied capitalized parameter values ("Moderate", "Dynamic") instead of the expected lowercase ("moderate", "dynamic"), causing a mismatch and no recognized function call despite otherwise correct tool selection and argument structure.

The agent added an unsupported "weatherDetail" parameter to the FlightStatus_checkFlightAndWeather function call, resulting in a signature mismatch with the expected parameters, which only accept "airportCode" and "flightNumber".
The agent called the correct function but omitted the required "ratingThreshold" parameter, failing to filter recommendations to only those with good ratings as requested.

The agent used "4.5" as the rating argument instead of the expected categorical value "high," resulting in a parameter mismatch and failure to invoke the required function with the correct input format.
